✅ 3. PROGRAM 1: BEFORE ROW TRIGGER (Validate Salary)
✔ Fixes:
IF syntax corrected
RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR corrected
Proper :NEW usage
SQL
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER trg_emp_before
BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE ON EMPLOYEE
FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
    IF :NEW.SALARY < 5000 THEN
        RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20010, 'Salary cannot be less than 5000');
    END IF;
END;
/
